main event: A witness observed an unidentified aerial object over La Grange, Illinois on September 15, 1963.
interesting points: The witness described the object as matching descriptions of UFOs reported in the area previously.
The witness estimated the object was about 1/2 mile high and 1/4 mile away.
The witness estimated the object's speed to be around 1/2 mile per hour.
The witness did not see the object through any optical aids like binoculars or a telescope.
The witness reported the sighting to the Air Force, who evaluated the object as a balloon.
